3. Access to services In order to permit you to access the Client Calibration Database, Cal‐Tek Co., Inc. will provide you with one or more access code(s) and password(s). You shall not divulge or disclose any access code or password to any person outside of your company. You may not use any access code or password should your employment with your current employer be terminated for any re ason. 
